  "description": "<p>分类: <a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/category/news/\" rel=\"tag\">科技新闻</a>, <a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/category/gaming/\" rel=\"tag\">游戏产品</a></p><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/2014/05/08/nintendo-is-making-entirely-new-consoles-for-emerging-market\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"http://o.aolcdn.com/hss/storage/midas/3c22baa41d8c483987df5ecbc1cc0cef/200099124/nintendo-wii-mini-handson.jpg\" /></a></div>\n<br />\n以任天堂的<a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/2014/05/07/nintendo-financial-results-2013-wii-u/\">现状</a>而言，他们今天所公布的决策，真的算是一个相当大胆，但也似乎不失为一个突破现状可能方案 -- 根据 Bloomberg 的报道指出，针对预算条件相对拮据的新兴市场，任天堂不想要将现有产品降低配备或 Cost down 来挤出一个更廉价的现有游戏机版本，反而决定要\"打造出一个全新的游戏主机\"。社长岩田聪在访谈中表示，与其推出现有产品的低价版本，倒不如发展一个从零开始考量价位平衡而生的全新产品。换句话说... 也就是 <a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/2013/09/04/nintendo-2ds-handson/\">2DS</a> <a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/2014/01/10/nintendo-record-3ds-game-sales/\">这个方向</a>吧？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n经由：<a href=\"http://www.engadget.com/2014/05/08/nintendo-is-making-entirely-new-consoles-for-emerging-market\">Engadget</a><br />\n引用来源：​<a href=\"http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2014-05-08/nintendo-plans-to-sell-new-consoles-for-emerging-markets-in-2015.html\">Bloomberg</a><p><h6 style=\"clear: both; padding: 8px 0 0 0; height: 2px; font-size: 1px; border: 0; margin: 0; padding: 0;\"></h6><a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/2014/05/08/nintendo-is-making-entirely-new-consoles-for-emerging-market/\" rel=\"bookmark\" title=\"Permanent link to this entry\">此文章网址</a>&nbsp;|&nbsp;<a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/forward/20882199/\" title=\"Send this entry to a friend via email\">转寄此文章</a>&nbsp;|&nbsp;<a href=\"http://cn.engadget.com/2014/05/08/nintendo-is-making-entirely-new-consoles-for-emerging-market/#comments\" title=\"View reader comments on this entry\">回应</a><hr size=\"1\" />", 
